text: José Luis Tamayo Terán (29 July 1858 - 7 July 1947) was President of Ecuador from 1 September 1920 to 31 August 1924. He was a member of the Ecuadorian Radical Liberal Party. ==Other websites== *Presidentes del Ecuador *Diccionario biográfico de Ecuador *Biografías y Vidas Category:1858 births Category:1947 deaths Category:Santa Elena Province Category:Presidents of Ecuador
